\ls3\ilvl0
\f1 \cf0 {\listtext	\'95	}\uc0\u9679 
\f0 	\cf2 The Challenge: You mentioned facing a libgl1 dependency error because the base Debian image changed. You solved this by explicitly installing the correct OpenGL libraries in the Dockerfile.\
