\pard\pardeftab720\ri0\sl276\slmult1\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0
\fs22 \cf0 {\listtext	4.	}"I built the image locally and pushed it to the cloud."\
{\listtext	5.	}This was a critical step where you handled cross-platform compatibility.\
